column16: Jay Bruce homers (18) on a line drive to right field.
Brandon Phillips flies out to left fielder Matt Holliday.
Devin Mesoraco homers (24) on a fly ball to left field.   Kristopher Negron scores.    Todd Frazier scores.

Chris Heisey singles on a soft line drive to right fielder Randal Grichuk.   Brayan Pena scores.    Devin Mesoraco scores.    Jason Bourgeois to 3rd.  Chris Heisey advances to 2nd, on a throwing error by right fielder Randal Grichuk.
Jason Bourgeois singles on a sharp line drive to right fielder Randal Grichuk.   Brayan Pena to 3rd.    Devin Mesoraco to 2nd.
Devin Mesoraco walks.   Brayan Pena to 2nd.
Todd Frazier pops out to shortstop Jhonny Peralta.
Brayan Pena singles on a soft line drive to center fielder Peter Bourjos.
